Company


Revoil Petroleum SA engages in marketing and sale of petroleum products.It operates through the following segments: Petroleum Products, Biofuels and Renewables Trade, and Investing in Seagoing Ships.The Petroleum Products segment buys and sells all types of petrol/gasoline and diesel.The Investing... Read more 



